<div class="title">Soma Analogue Potions</div>
<div class="substance">Amanita muscaria & Brugmansia</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Quetzalcoatl&Exact=1">Quetzalcoatl</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Quetzalcoatl. "Soma Analogue Potions: An Experience with Amanita muscaria & Brugmansia (exp3863)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Mar 6, 2001. erowid.org/exp/3863</div>

<br/>



<div class="report-text-surround">
